data.title: 2014) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Wilmer Bud Arthur Wagner, of Hermantown, died peacefully Thursday, Jan. 16, 2014 at Bayshore Residence in Duluth, with family by his side.  Bud was born on June 14, 1919 in Hermantown to Henry and Elsie Wagner, and was raised on the family farm.  He attended Washington School, and served in the Civilian Conservation...
